{"about_the_game":"<strong><i>Minimal Slide</i></strong> is a sliding puzzle game rich of features and with puzzles for players of every skill level.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/MS-level-play.gif?t=1727975418\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/MS-levels.png?t=1727975418\" /><br><br>The game features <strong>over 100 levels</strong>, divided in three difficulties, using many different types of tiles from classic tetrominoes to more complex shapes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/MS-improve.png?t=1727975418\" /><br><br>Beating a level is not always the end of it: try to complete it with the least amount of moves to reach the <i>star score</i>. You'll need to come up with new strategies to succeed, uncovering the hidden depth of the game!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/MS-level-end.gif?t=1727975418\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/MS-customize.png?t=1727975418\" /><br><br>The first time you beat a level, you earn coins you can use to unlock colors, textures and more with which you can <strong>customize</strong> the game's appearance. If you're lucky, you can even win rare special sets with unique visuals and sounds for the tiles!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/Ms-randomize.png?t=1727975418\" /><br><br>Can't decide how to customize the game? Use the <i>randomizer</i> to randomly change visuals and sounds. You can even choose to randomize any combination of them each time you start a level!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/MS-carousel.gif?t=1727975418\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/MS-features.png?t=1727975418\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 100 levels divided in three difficulties. </li><li>50+ customize options. </li><li>Randomizer for the game's appearance. </li><li>Various statistics about beaten levels. </li><li>Original soundtrack and sound effects.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Sliding into Action","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3163570/78d191f1d5311fe708cc25144853b8683eabcd0f.jpg"},{"name":"One in Seven","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3163570/42925bdd90986a563a6c99f3daf5582e920b6431.jpg"},{"name":"Not a Beginner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3163570/e51899534170dd6c27061bee1ff9677da12e357f.jpg"},{"name":"Shallow Success","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3163570/eabe35391b584c63fb43fa971d3027806d8d5c32.jpg"},{"name":"Glance at the Sky","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3163570/8b2dc65483bc0cb8f73763e01b717dbf318356ae.jpg"},{"name":"Lights from Effort","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3163570/1f7a110efee9aa2e3faf7db7009a5d09a84e289e.jpg"},{"name":"Your choice...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3163570/bc6d97b86bd0a16bd40f8e416118c1b428646aed.jpg"},{"name":"Some Variety","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3163570/1e5bfc6f94d991b0d7e7ec682fb3ae42b03d0283.jpg"},{"name":"More Diversity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3163570/2ef09959b836bccb7557979d449f7e0451b4e6f1.jpg"},{"name":"Luck or Diligence","path":"https://cdn.a